Dictionar v2.20

English: Sorry, no documentation yet. 

This is a Word-Database Program, for *YOUR* own words. The program can test
Your knowledge. The program comes with 3000 Word-Pairs (German/Hungarian).
There is a multi-language-support, so you can create a Tibetian-Madagaskar
dictionary too, just duplicape the NewLanguage drawer, and rename it
"Tibetian". ;-), after that, you can select it in the "Group" menu.

**** There is not included:
                - An ENGLISH version. *** If there are enough requests, I will
translate it ***
                - You can use the German or the Hungarian ( :-) ) version!

Reach me: Norbert Makk nmakk@kabel.datatrans.hu

PS:

NO, Im not a programmer, it is just made for fun. There is a PC version too,
but not yet publicated.
